{"name":"Notify the team on new events with Gmail hands-free","nodes":[{"parameters":{"httpMethod":"POST","path":"wf06019-job","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.webhook","typeVersion":2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"5b32a6bc-984b-4084-9ec1-5eac53669e42","name":"Receive Inbound Webhook","webhookId":"1e271d69-567c-46af-94bb-25a4e27dbacb"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"77bd047a-3de2-409f-b033-a551e3f39017","name":"jobId","value":"={{ $json.body?.jobId || $json.body?.id }}","type":"string"},{"id":"be957af1-daca-4dc8-a1e1-62290732b316","name":"kind","value":"={{ $json.body?.type || 'default' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"548ad34d-f9c8-4a61-842d-9236848318ed","name":"payload","value":"={{ JSON.stringify($json.body || $json) }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[54,400],"id":"25ea4974-70ee-4313-8534-ba08ec4d91f9","name":"Map to Canonical Schema"},{"parameters":{"rules":{"values":[{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"4bbee3cb-b3ff-413d-aa26-96120785f63c","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind }}","rightValue":"created","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"created"},{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"f9ab134c-12f6-4174-a177-709cc55d9e54","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind }}","rightValue":"updated","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"updated"}]},"options":{"fallbackOutput":"extra"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.switch","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[378,400],"id":"1ab250df-5062-402d-ba6c-00ec6e43a019","name":"Route by Event Kind"},{"parameters":{"operation":"appendOrUpdate","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Job Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":["jobId"],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[702,130],"id":"1860c2b4-82a3-4c7f-addd-c9e19f135ba0","name":"Handle 'created' → Google Sheets","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"method":"POST","url":"https://api.example.com/v1/jobs","sendBody":true,"specifyBody":"json","jsonBody":"={{ JSON.stringify($json) }}","options":{"timeout":20000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[1026,640],"id":"9467fcf6-b434-4134-aa56-133a2cb6191b","name":"Handle 'updated' → Forward API","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Job Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[1350,1150],"id":"3b459129-ef3e-4cb6-bf6b-ebd93e0c4d5f","name":"Log Unrecognized Kind","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[1998,400],"id":"450756ff-8c9d-4ae2-adbc-a8a2989b2f88","name":"Consolidate Handling"},{"parameters":{"respondWith":"json","responseBody":"={{ { \"ok\": true } }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[2970,400],"id":"e50be6e2-6a23-4d3b-9b48-41722240614d","name":"Respond with Outcome"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"632f749f-8c2c-4a09-bd5b-4a51e968054e","name":"pipeline","value":"Triggers","type":"string"},{"id":"a3af3c78-b6d4-423f-ad1b-bfaf91672083","name":"version","value":"2.0","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[3294,400],"id":"12a97397-6223-4e75-b74f-28140cdbe855","name":"Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf06019-job`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Map to Canonical Schema","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"9a386913-f8cc-7e56-8172-9e6ddfc26799","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Map to Canonical Schema\n\nShapes the item: writes `jobId`, `kind`, `payload`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Route by Event Kind","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"5f38d4e3-6b9d-7712-bda2-4ed378861df8","name":"Note: Map to Canonical Schema"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Event Kind\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: created, updated + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Handle 'created' → Google Sheets · ②→ Handle 'updated' → Forward API · ③→ Log Unrecognized Kind","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"fe516b23-9ae3-5568-0e74-e80cb71abce8","name":"Note: Route by Event Kind"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'created' → Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,250],"id":"1cd2a9ae-83ef-c582-2c99-0c46f0a0edf6","name":"Note: Handle 'created' → Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'updated' → Forward API\n\nPOST https://api.example.com/v1/jobs — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,760],"id":"2cbfba63-4478-aac5-dc49-aa30de404f0d","name":"Note: Handle 'updated' → Forward API"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Log Unrecognized Kind\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1270],"id":"72969fc1-117e-9a9c-d726-3c538b7cdde5","name":"Note: Log Unrecognized Kind"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Consolidate Handling\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Respond with Outcome","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"dbd88368-d527-1b0a-f8f3-244b0369c077","name":"Note: Consolidate Handling"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Respond with Outcome\n\nSends the HTTP 200 response back to the caller — keep this fast; heavy work happens after/async.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"e31d04e5-5efe-1e1a-119a-96899e48387d","name":"Note: Respond with Outcome"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"514aab1b-5dd9-e43b-3c2e-8611c7b2ab6b","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Notify the team on new events with Gmail hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** Event Notification · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nNotify the team on new events with Gmail hands-free. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual triggers is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Map to Canonical Schema → Route by Event Kind → Handle 'created' → Google Sheets → Consolidate Handling → Respond with Outcome → Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to event notification without manual effort\n- Anyone automating triggers in productivity\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Improves response time\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"c4f311a4-e9b1-c571-50c8-d56b90c7cb38","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"bd80acd5-4e10-9e91-38c0-d05ef8e82c80","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your triggers process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-290],"id":"dee5755c-78a2-36e9-f954-bd4296f32d98","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Map to Canonical Schema","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Map to Canonical Schema":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Event Kind","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Event Kind":{"main":[[{"node":"Handle 'created' → Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Handle 'updated' → Forward API","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Log Unrecognized Kind","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Handle 'created' → Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Handle 'updated' → Forward API":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Log Unrecognized Kind":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":2}]]},"Consolidate Handling":{"main":[[{"node":"Respond with Outcome","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Respond with Outcome":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"856be97c-5e09-4c1e-bc23-0a6a3ce1b94e","id":"FDX06019"}